<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:courier;font-size:xx-small;">Three guesses, and then it is destroyed.<br>
 <br>
Born at the same time as the world, destined to live as long as the world, and yet never five weeks old.  What is it?</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
The man looks to you in fear, and awaits your next action.  <p>-----------------<br>
